  <name>Copy That v1.25.0</name>
  <summary>Byte-exact cross-platform file copier</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Copy That v1.25.0 is a lightweight, cross-platform, async, byte-exact
      file and folder copier. Matches every TeraCopy feature while staying
      as fast as — or faster than — Explorer, Finder, cp, and rsync for
      typical desktop workloads.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Verify after copy (CRC32, MD5, SHA-1/256/512, xxHash3, BLAKE3)</li>
      <li>Reflink clones on Btrfs, XFS, APFS, ReFS</li>
      <li>SQLite history + lifetime totals dashboard</li>
      <li>Multi-pass secure delete</li>
      <li>18-language UI</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
